title: 5 Shekels
author: stampedechive
pages:
#- There was once a large town by the name of /pol/ynesia or /pol/town as many referred to it. Resource Town was its common name amongst the Channers due to the vast amounts of resources that had been dug up by the hard-working /pol/ynesians. 
#- The town had a decent population and was home to the great /pol/ castle. A mighty structure built single-handedly by the infamous Outcast_Mephisto. It was another successful day in /pol/ynesia as any other. Resources were being mined and progress was
#- being made. When suddenly, there was a raider threat. It appeared that about 9 raiders from the land of Uguu were fast approaching the town. Many fled to the bunker and took as many valuables as they could to log off with them. Others stayed to fight.
#- Those who did stay to fight knew that it would not be an easy battle, but their 
